
 A bunch of scripts to test various text mining features.
 Type perl file_name from the command line to run the test.

 File		Description
 --------------------------------------------------------------------
 cluster.pl	Test clustering code
 db_test.pl	Test session management 
 match.pl	Verify the text_match function
 phrases.pl	Test phrase extraction
 pos_test.pl 	Test parts of speech tagging
 sense.pl	Disambiguate words with multiple senses
 summary.pl	Test the summarizer
 test_ent.pl	Test the entity extractor
 tgen.pl	Random sentence generator
 tsplit.pl	Test splitting of text into sentences
 vectors.pl	Generate vectors using different indexing methods
 words.pl	Test other functions
